data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful property right by Sioux Passage Park. If you love nature; this is the property for you! Open floor plan, 4 Bed, 3 full bath home sitting on 2.16 park-like acres. Updates galore! Waiting on your finishing touches! Roof and gutters-2yrs old, cozy wood burning fireplace in living room, newer flooring and toilet in hall bath, newer flooring, vanity and toilet in basement bath, new lighting throughout the whole house, Nest thermostat, Ring doorbell, updated both electrical panels, new kitchen hood, 2 fans with retractable blades, cabinets, sink with smart faucet and newer flooring. HVAC-6 yrs old and routinely serviced, newer outdoor lighting and updated mailbox. Newer flooring in lower level finished recreation room and sleeping or workout room with attached full bath. Additional bonus room, unfinished storage area, and additional workshop room! 2-car oversized garage and plenty of space to spread out! Must see!  Seller Credit for 2-1 Interest Buy Down
